    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy\u2014meticulously cared for, kept spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no stories, just a stunning car waiting for its next adventure. I\u2019d love for you to come see it in person because pictures really don't do this gem justice. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
