    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, so you\u2019re getting a total gem that drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that's been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
